15. The method of claim 13, further comprising transmitting the trained machine learning model to the user device over the communication network.
16. The method of claim 13, wherein the marker indicates a likelihood that the measurement goal will be satisfied in the future.
17. The method of claim 13, wherein the second sensor data comprises data captured at a time that is partially through a predetermined time period corresponding to the measurement goal, wherein the marker indicates a likelihood that the measurement goal will be satisfied by an end of the predetermined time period.
